                <a id="logo-name-site" title="CSCE Library" href="/">CSCE Department Library</a>
            </h1>
            <div id="UNT" class=" col-sm-4">
                <a id="unt-logo" class="pull-right" title="UNT | A Green Light to Greatness" href="http://www.unt.edu">
